\pm\\; \\text{therefore}\\; \\pm)$</think> <answer> <p>Two solutions</p> </answer>", "truth": "1", "reward_format": 1.0, "reward_answer": 0.0, "reward_total": 0.0}, {"prompt": "A conversation between User and Assistant. The User asks a question, and the Assistant solves it. The Assistant first thinks about the reasoning process in the mind and then provides the User with the answer. The reasoning process is enclosed within <think> </think> and answer is enclosed within <answer> </answer> tags, respectively, i.e., <think> reasoning process here </think> <answer> answer here </answer>.\nUser: Two interior angles of a convex pentagon are right angles and the other three interior angles are congruent. In degrees, what is the measure of one of the three congruent interior angles?\nAssistant: <think>", "response": " <img src=\"https://latex.codecogs.com\u9e21\u86cb<img src=\"https://latex.codecogs.comLaTeX%20ntag%20\u96b6%3A%20\")(ABCDE)%3B discipline%3A%20%28%28%20representing%20the%20diagram%29%20%28A%20B%20C%20D%20E%29%7Today%20we%20will%20be%20given%20this%20diagram%20representing%20a%20pentagon%20with%205%20points%20and%205%20lines%20connected%20them%3B%20as%20we%20can%20see%2C%20the%20diagram%20represents%20a%20pentagon%20with%205%20blue%20dots%20and%205%20lines%20connecting%20them%3Blittle%20word%20in%20the%20diagram%20is%20imperative%20and%20helpful%3B%20we%20can%20see%20that%20two%20lines%20intersect%20at%20'B'and%20%28%20so%20we%20know%20that%20%36%3B%3Bg%3B&katex_proxy_id=%3Dkatex%7B%7Bimage%20%7B07%20co%2D.html%7D%7D%3B&katex_input%3Dcd%7B.\" onclick=\u201dthis%3B\u201d> <img src=\"https://latex.codecogs.comL aesthetic=%20ge%20br%2C%20height%20%3D0.5em%20style%3C TexasID%3A dc%20style%3D%20 Colorado\u5d1f%20d%206%20!_DOWNWRFinal answer should be 135 <End>7\r</img> </img> <img src=\"https://latex.codecogs.comLaTeX%20ntag%20\u96b6%3A%20)%2C%20where%2C%20the%20two%20radii%20of%20the%20circumctheirm%20intersect%20%20%28dx%20and%20dx%29%20%2C%20then%20%7B.\" onclic